	* configure.ac: Post-release version suffix added.

2013-05-19  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	=== First release for babel-thai ===

	* configure.ac, NEWS:
	=== Version 1.0.0 ===

2013-05-17  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Add babel-thai CTAN zip preparation.

	* Makefile.am:
	  - Add dist-babel-thai target for preparing upload Zip file for CTAN.

2013-05-16  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Drop sync-babel script.

	* scripts/Makefile.am, -scripts/sync-babel:
	  - Drop sync-babel script, as we are merging into it.

2013-05-16  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Drop obsolete thswitch.sty.

	* babel/Makefile.am -babel/thswitch.sty:
	  - Drop thswitch.sty. It won't be included in the upcoming
	    babel-thai CTAN upload.

2013-05-16  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Optionally exclude hyphenation source.

	As a transition to hyph-utf8 in CTAN, exclude hyphenation patterns
	and source from the distribution, while still provide an option
	'--enable-hyphenation' to include it for some legacy TeX Live.
	This way, we can still keep the source in VCS during the transition.

	* configure.ac:
	  - Add --enable-hyphenation option, with AM_CONDITIONAL.
	  - Also check availability of hyphen/ in distribution before
	    actually enabling hyphenation as instructed.
	  - Check for patgen only if hyphenation is enabled.
	  - Generate hyphen/Makefile only if hyphenation is enabled.
	* Makefile.am:
	  - Include README.hyphen and hyphen/ subdir, both in building
	    process and in distribution, only if hyphenation is enabled.

2013-03-31  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Some refinements.

	* babel/thai.dtx:
	  - Wrap lines to 80 columns.
	  - Use 2 spaces after fullstops.
	  - Make \@afterindent... mentionings in the doc verbatim.

2013-03-31  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Fix compilation error in the last commit.

	* babel/thai.dtx:
	  - Close \changes{} added by me before committing Pruet's patch
	    in last commit.

2013-03-31  Pruet Boonma  <pruetboonma@gmail.com>

	Add thaiindentfirst option to force first paragraph indentation.

	* babel/thai.dtx:
	  - Add thaiindentfirst option with documentation.
	  - Bump file version to 1.8.

2013-03-13  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Limit scope of emergencystretch within Thai language.

	* babel/thai.dtx:
	  - Instead of directly \setlength{}, do it via \extrasthai and
	    restore it in \noextrasthai.

2013-03-12  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Fix crash when using thainumber with section-less doc class.

	'thainumber' option is found to crash on, 'letter' document class,
	which has no 'section' counters.

	* babel/thai.dtx:
	  - Define \@overridecommand{} helper macro which checks for existence
	    of the command before renewing it.
	  - Use \@overridecommand instead of \renewcommand on counters.

2013-02-17  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan  <thep@linux.thai.net>

	Update TODO.

	* TODO:
	  - Drop finished hyphenation wish list.
	  - Drop unclear wish list on multi-pass word segmentation.

